description:
A privet 2000 SQFT Duplex in a beautiful 1890 Brownstone at the Prospect Lefferts Gardens of Brooklyn.
Steps from the prospect park, the Botanical Gardens, the new ice ring and the Brooklyn Zoo.
20 min subway ride to downtown Manhattan.

The apt is completely modern with 2 Bedrooms and 2 full bath.
Full kitchen and recreation space as well as a big leaving room open to a back garden.
The duplex has Central Air, full heat system and laundry room.

You have your own apt and back yard use.

This is an upcoming neighborhood with allot of new coffee shops bakeries and restaurants 20 min subway ride to downtown Manhattan.
